<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>その消毒、次亜塩素で大丈夫ですか？｜水中除菌タブレット クリアンス（CREINS）</title>
  <meta name="description" content="クリアンス（CREINS）は水に投入するだけで二酸化塩素を発生させる水中衛生管理タブレット。温浴施設・スポーツ施設をはじめ、全国100ヶ所以上の施設で導入されています。">
  <meta name="keywords" content="レジオネラ属菌対策,二酸化塩素,クリアンス,CREINS,次亜塩素,温浴施設,水質衛生管理,バイオフィルム,pH">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700;900&family=Montserrat:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0 }

    :root {
      --primary:    #5bc3ec;
      --primary-sub:#2ca6e0;
      --navy:       #084d9f;
      --navy-mid:   #2b5ea8;
      --aqua-bg:    rgba(91, 195, 236, 0.10);
      --off-white:  #f7f7f7;
      --light-blue: #fafafa;
      --blue-gray:  #d4dfed;
      --border:     #d9e7f1;
      --border-mid: #c2d6e5;
      --text:       #333333;
      --text-mid:   #556270;
      --text-light: #7f8a94;
      --white:      #fff;
      --green:      #1d7a4a;
      --green-bg:   #eaf4ee;
      --red:        #b03030;
      --container:  1200px;
      --section:    90px 0;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; font-size: 16px }

    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.8;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      background: var(--white);
    }

    img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: inherit }
    strong { font-weight: 700 }

    .container { max-width: var(--container); margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px }

    section { padding: var(--section) }

    h2.section-title {
      font-size: 2.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      letter-spacing: .04em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      line-height: 1.45;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-sub {
      color: var(--text-light);
      font-size: .9rem;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .divider {
      width: 40px;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--primary);
      margin: 16px 0 40px;
    }

    .divider.center { margin: 16px auto 40px }

    /* ── Buttons ── */
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--primary);
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 16px 62px 16px 36px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .25s;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(91, 195, 236, .25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: .9rem;
      padding: 14px 58px 14px 32px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1.5px solid var(--primary);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .25s;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      position: relative;
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .btn-outline-white {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--white);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 16px 62px 16px 36px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .25s;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      position: relative;
    }

    .btn-outline-white:hover {
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--navy);
      border-color: var(--white);
    }

    .btn-primary::after,
    .btn-outline::after,
    .btn-outline-white::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: 24px;
      top: 50%;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg);
      border-top: 1.5px solid currentColor;
      border-right: 1.5px solid currentColor;
    }

    .btn-primary-light {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      background: var(--white);
      color: var(--navy);
      font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1rem;
      padding: 16px 62px 16px 36px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--white);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .25s;
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      position: relative;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, .14);
    }

    .btn-primary-light:hover {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--white);
      box-shadow: none;
    }

    .btn-primary-light::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      right: 24px;
      top: 50%;
      width: 10px;
      height: 10px;
      transform: translateY(-50%) rotate(45deg);
      border-top: 1.5px solid currentColor;
      border-right: 1.5px solid currentColor;
    }

    .floating-cta {
      position: fixed;
      right: 24px;
      top: 50%;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      z-index: 95;
      width: 188px;
      padding: 16px 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.94);
      border: 1px solid rgba(91, 195, 236, .35);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 42px rgba(8, 77, 159, .14);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: opacity .25s ease, transform .25s ease, visibility .25s ease;
    }

    .floating-cta.is-hidden {
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      pointer-events: none;
      transform: translateY(-50%) translateX(12px);
    }

    .floating-cta-label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .64rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--primary-sub);
    }

    .floating-cta-copy {
      font-size: .78rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }

    .floating-cta .btn-primary {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 54px;
      padding: 14px 52px 14px 24px;
      font-size: .88rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(91, 195, 236, .22);
    }

    /* ── Header ── */
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,.96), rgba(255,255,255,.88));
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(217, 231, 241, .85);
      padding: 14px 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(8, 77, 159, .06);
    }

    .header .container {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .header-logo {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .header-logo-main {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }

    .header-logo-sub {
      font-size: .72rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      letter-spacing: .02em;
    }

    .header-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px }

    .header-tel {
      font-size: .85rem;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    }

    .header-tel-label {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
      font-size: .7rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1px;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(91,195,236,.20), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(255,255,255,1) 0%, rgba(250,250,250,1) 48%, rgba(212,223,237,.55) 100%);
      min-height: calc(100vh - 82px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 56px 0 72px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(380px, 1.1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-text {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.92);
      border: 1px solid rgba(217, 231, 241, .9);
      border-radius: 40px;
      padding: 48px 44px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 54px rgba(8, 77, 159, .08);
    }

    .hero-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--primary-sub);
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      padding: 7px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.75);
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 4vw, 3.55rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: var(--navy);
      letter-spacing: .02em;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .hero h1 .accent { color: var(--primary-sub) }

    .hero p.lead {
      font-size: 1.03rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 1.95;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      max-width: 520px;
    }

    .hero p.lead .lead-line { display: block }
    .nowrap { white-space: nowrap }

    .hero-stats {
      display: flex;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      padding-top: 32px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(91, 195, 236, .35);
    }

    .hero-stat-item {}

    .hero-stat-num {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.4rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-sub);
      line-height: 1;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-stat-unit {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-stat-label {
      font-size: .78rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 6px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .hero-stat-note {
      font-size: .68rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .hero-stat-copy {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: .95rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1.8;
      max-width: 220px;
    }

    /* Hero visual side */
    .hero-visual { position: relative }

    .hero-img-wrap {
      border-radius: 44px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(8,77,159,.12), rgba(91,195,236,.26));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.65);
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(8, 77, 159, .14);
    }

    .hero-img-placeholder {
      height: 520px;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(8,77,159,.92), rgba(44,166,224,.88));
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-img-placeholder img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .hero-stat-badge {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 28px;
      left: 28px;
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid rgba(91, 195, 236, .35);
      border-radius: 26px;
      padding: 20px 26px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
    }

    .hero-stat-badge .num {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      line-height: 1;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-stat-badge .desc {
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      margin-top: 4px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-cta-note {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: .78rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    /* ── Pain ── */
    .pain { background: var(--white) }

    .pain-intro {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .pain-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 24px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .pain-card {
      background: var(--off-white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 28px;
      padding: 40px 36px;
      transition: background .2s, border-color .2s, transform .2s;
    }

    .pain-card:hover {
      background: var(--white);
      border-bottom-color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .pain-num {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--navy);
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      display: block;
    }

    .pain-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .pain-card p {
      font-size: .88rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 1.9;
    }

    .pain-data-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--primary-sub);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    /* ── About ── */
    .about { background: var(--off-white) }

    .about-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
      gap: 72px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-text h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .about-text p {
      font-size: .95rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-features {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .about-feature {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      background: var(--white);
      border-left: 3px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 0 18px 18px 0;
    }

    .about-feature-icon {
      width: 20px;
      height: 20px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      margin-top: 1px;
    }

    .about-feature-text {
      font-size: .88rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .about-feature-text strong {
      color: var(--navy);
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .about-img-wrap {
      border-radius: 2px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    /* ── Compare ── */
    .compare { background: var(--white) }

    .compare-header {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .compare-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto }

    .compare-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

    .compare-table th {
      padding: 16px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: .82rem;
      letter-spacing: .04em;
    }

    .compare-table th:first-child { text-align: left }

    .compare-table thead tr {
      background: var(--navy);
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .compare-table thead th.col-creins {
      background: var(--primary);
    }

    .compare-table tbody td {
      padding: 16px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text-mid);
      vertical-align: middle;
    }

    .compare-table tbody td:first-child {
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      font-size: .88rem;
    }

    .compare-table tbody tr:hover td { background: var(--off-white) }

    .compare-table .col-creins {
      background: rgba(91, 195, 236, 0.12);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
    }

    .compare-table .col-creins:hover { background: rgba(91, 195, 236, 0.18) }

    .val-good { color: var(--green); font-weight: 700 }
    .val-bad  { color: var(--red); font-weight: 500 }
    .val-mid  { color: var(--text-mid); font-weight: 500 }

    .val-good::before { content: '○ '; font-size: .85em }
    .val-bad::before  { content: '△ '; font-size: .85em }

    .compare-note {
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 14px;
      text-align: right;
    }

    /* ── Science ── */
    .science { background: var(--white); }

    .science-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
      gap: 64px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .science-text p {
      font-size: .93rem;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .science-note {
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 24px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 16px;
    }

    /* pH Chart */
    .ph-chart {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 32px 28px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      box-shadow: 0 14px 32px rgba(8, 77, 159, .05);
    }

    .ph-chart-title {
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .ph-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 52px 1fr 52px;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .ph-row-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .75rem;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      text-align: right;
    }

    .ph-bar-bg {
      height: 24px;
      background: rgb(212, 223, 237);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .ph-bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      transition: width .8s ease;
    }

    .ph-bar-fill.c-high { background: var(--primary-sub) }
    .ph-bar-fill.c-mid  { background: #8cc9e6 }
    .ph-bar-fill.c-low  { background: var(--navy-mid) }

    .ph-row-val {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .ph-chart-source {
      font-size: .7rem;
      color: var(--text-light);
      margin-top: 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Case Study ── */
    .case { background: var(--off-white) }

    .case-inner {
      background: var(--white);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 34px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .case-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--navy-mid));
      padding: 24px 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .case-label {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      padding: 4px 10px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .case-header h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--white);
    }

    .case-body { padding: 40px }

    .case-detail-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: .88rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .case-detail-table tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border) }

    .case-detail-table th {
      width: 180px;
      padding: 14px 20px;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--navy);
      background: var(--off-white);
      font-size: .83rem;
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .case-detail-table td {
      padding: 14px 20px;
      color: var(--text-mid);
      line-height: 1.8;
    }

    .case-timeline {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .case-step {
      padding: 28px 24px;
      position: relative;
      border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .case-step:last-child { border-right: none }

    .case-step-num {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
